data.description: Popular Amerillo model home - 3 bedrooms in a split floor plan. Airconditioning replaced in 2015 and the roof replaced and the BOND HAS BEEN PAID - The home will be unfurnished ready to make your own.  There is a Florida room off of the dining room that is bright and airy a place to sit and relax.  The interior laundry room is also a plus.  The location is perfect with a quick ride to Spanish Springs Square or in the other direction to Lake Sumter Landing.  Golf courses around the corner and others a short golf cart ride.
